---
// SelfIntroCard.astro
const title = "About Me";
---
<div class="intro-card">
    <div class="content">
        <h2>{title}</h2>
        <p>
            Hi there! I am a senior undergraduate at the 
            <a href= "https://me.sjtu.edu.cn/"> School of Mechanical Engineering, Shanghai Jiao Tong University</a>, 
            advised by Prof. 
            <a href= "https://me.sjtu.edu.cn/teacher_directory1/shengxinjun.html">Xinjun Sheng</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Previously, under the guidance of Dr. 
            <a href= "https://psy.sjtu.edu.cn/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=show&catid=11221&id=208">Binglei Zhao</a> and Prof. 
            <a href= "https://bme.shanghaitech.edu.cn/2021/0326/c8204a62068/page.htm">Han Zhang</a>, 
            I had the privilege of exploring the mysteries of the human brain through cognitive science and neuroimaging.
        </p>
        <p>
            Right now, my research interests lie in dexterous manipulation and human-robot interaction. 
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.intro-card {
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); 
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}
.intro-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.content {
    padding: 50px;
    text-align: left;
}

h2 {
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-size: 2rem;
}

a {
    color:rgba(0,0,0,1);
    text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

p {
    margin: 1em 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}
</style>